des: HB RADIO, Las Vegas #1 hip hop internet station is owned & operated by Domus Media Group & was founded in 2014 by David Hart "Dj Hartbreaker". We are an independent internet radio station that shines light on mainstream hip hop music, news and also showcases independent artists. HB RADIO has weekly programmed mix-shows from some of vegas' most talented dj's & on air personalities. From your favorite wake up morning shows to your eccentric night mix-shows, we have something for all of our listeners.
